'''Paris Howe Strewe''' played [[Théodred]] in ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''. He is not an actor, and his only other credit in filmmaking is "lighting assistant" on [http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0138602/ Memory & Desire], starring [[Norman Forsey]] and [[Ian Hughes]]. He had some popularity after the movies came out, but both fansites<sup>[http://www.geocities.com/parishowestrewe/][http://www.fansites.com/details.asp?id=102087]</sup> are offline now.
